{"tid":326373,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"短線炒返轉鷹君0041","createTime":"2017-07-18T02:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T17:59:10.000Z","uid":121784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80768fd7d6660fc26ae8fb673964d73d2dc01fc0","tid":326373,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"鷹君趁樓市升到癲, 賣朗豪坊辦公大樓, 所以計下數, 入市炒返轉!<br />\n<br />\n鷹君 --(65.62%)--&gt; 冠君 --(100%)--&gt; 朗豪坊<br />\n<br />\n冠君<br />\n股價: 5.93<br />\n市值: 334.65億<br />\nP/B: 0.68<br />\n朗豪坊售價: 245億<br />\n<br />\n冠君資產總值 = 334.65/0.68 = 492.13億<br />\n出售朗豪坊後: 247億固定資產 + 245億現金<br />\n若P(固定資產)/B不變, 市值 = 247*0.68 +245 = 413億<br />\n鷹君所佔 = 413*0.6562 = 271億<br />\n鷹君原來所佔 = 334.65*0.6562 = 220億<br />\n<br />\n鷹君<br />\n股價 = 41.850<br />\n市值: 287.83億<br />\nP/B: 0.508<br />\n<br />\n鷹君資產總值 = 287.83/0.508 = 566.6億<br />\n出售後, 資產總值 = 566.6 - 220 + 271 = 617.6億<br />\n假設P/B不變, 股價 = 41.85 * 617.6 / 566.6 = $45.6"},{"pid":"a1c74c7ba25599fdfff647a15d6b8ff77650d5d6","tid":326373,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"留名arbitrage"},{"pid":"6b8fb0faa6f150f15f11908eb809e6ea623050b7","tid":326373,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"43.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ab6a00476a36082b2d876f8f1477704044a6b2","tid":326373,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:27:46.000Z","msg":"唔知樓主係咪計錯數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身朗豪坊係2778的book係值85億。如果245億賣出，即係2778本book會由之前約500億收成500+（245-85）=660億<br />\n<br />\n即係用番0.68xPB, 2778的市值應該值245+(660-245)*0.68= 527億，前提係果245億會派出黎<br />\n<br />\n跟住鷹君值幾錢可以參考番樓主的計法"},{"pid":"0b4e828d1c0d89a24144a7f7ff40f2443d8ceeb2","tid":326373,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知樓主係咪計錯數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身朗豪坊係2778的book係值85億。如果245億賣出，即係2778本book會由之前約500億收成500+（245-85）=660億<br />\n<br />\n即係用番0.68xPB, 2778的市值應該值245+(660-245)*0.68= 527億，前提係果245億會派出黎<br />\n<br />\n跟住鷹君值幾錢可以參考番樓主的計法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks~<br />\n因為我係aastock搵料, 無睇到原本係book值幾錢XD"},{"pid":"88f352ed515772eff635c432b6f502f4ddc51649","tid":326373,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"今日又一枝陽燭爆上, 就快到價啦!"},{"pid":"7bdbd8a54c75239940909269f85fc664fd1f2c88","tid":326373,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"炒高完最後決定唔賣會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7279a7e6058ef93ddaa7738d9dece2a29984185f","tid":326373,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"咁耐都未有消息應該賣唔成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}